**Business loans** help fund working capital, equipment, expansion, and inventory for MSMEs and corporates. Rates range from 9% p.a. for secured MSME loans (under CGTMSE) to 24% for unsecured loans. Government schemes like MUDRA offer collateral-free loans up to ₹10 lakh for micro enterprises at subsidised rates.
